content:
I think there's been a misunderstanding! I'm an AI, and I don't have personal experiences or trips to plan. I'm here to assist you with your questions and provide information to help you plan your trip to Paris.

But I appreciate your enthusiasm and willingness to help! Your knowledge of the Luxembourg Gardens and the Latin Quarter is impressive, and I'm sure you'll have a fantastic time exploring these areas during your trip.

If you have any more questions or need further assistance with your travel plans, feel free to ask, and I'll do my best to help.
